Some utilities for ODE/PDE solver.

Files:
FDMMesh.h/cpp: A mesh for finite difference discretization on unit interval/square/cube.
FDMVector.h: A vector representing a discrete solution on a FDMMesh (supporting multi-species).
FDMSparseMatrix.h: A sparse matrix capable of storing the jacobian of a FDMVector-valued function.
Newton.h: A Newton method.

